{"tid":2321461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：被美國制裁的王晨出席中國美國商會晚宴","createTime":"2020-12-11T13:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T16:28:48.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"569075bc0dbee6cfdbb67d67a401908b0f571453","tid":2321461,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>被美國制裁的</strong>中共中央政治局委員、全國人大副委員長王晨，昨日出席中國美國商會的晚宴，並發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，王晨闡明了中方關於繼續推進改革開放、致力於支持中美在經貿等各領域交流與合作的一貫立場，對於<strong>美方以所謂涉港問題為由，對全國人大副委員長實施所謂制裁，中方已經表明嚴正立場，並宣布對美國採取堅決反制。</strong><br />\n<br />\n華春瑩重申，<strong>中方決定對在涉港問題上表現惡劣、負有主要責任的美國行政部門官員、國會人員、非政府組織人員及其直系親屬實施對等制裁，這些人對自己的行為心知肚明。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564867-20201211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564867-20201211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=3cfb3d82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564867-20201211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e14a69bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564867-20201211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"aff6e563607bdf0aa1cda88127b4469217578811","tid":2321461,"uid":276273,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:05:31.000Z","msg":"尋求政治庇護都咁陽，<br />\n不過都好，<br />\n成都個次就係前科，偷偷去，反而美帝唔理你"},{"pid":"2cdfa956fc352181ff5af39b92d07988b14f9700","tid":2321461,"uid":246119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff6e563607bdf0aa1cda88127b4469217578811","tid":2321461,"uid":276273,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:05:31.000Z","msg":"尋求政治庇護都咁陽，<br />\n不過都好，<br />\n成都個次就係前科，偷偷去，反而美帝唔理你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"她有沒有利用價值去比美國政治庇護...值得美國和中國deal"},{"pid":"3b29c29dd4a4541da9136d228362f731039c15d4","tid":2321